name: ARETHA
description:
Collage piece.
2048x2048

This is my work for the #hen500k, I really wanted to create something new but I chose this piece from 2018, specifically it is a cover that I had created on request for an artist called Cookin Soul for a material that he was going to publish on the occasion of the death of Aretha Franklin, unfortunately that material never saw the light due to issues of his record label beyond my control. I chose it because it is one of my favorite works and I didn't want it to be forgotten.
